{"tid":650300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同另一半/朋友出街撞到佢既朋友，個朋友當你唔存在","createTime":"2018-05-02T08:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T09:03:14.000Z","uid":10582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21663c3595073cab0020566a0a31dee76040b8ed","tid":650300,"uid":10582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"有時同另一半或者朋友出街，行行下會撞到佢地既朋友，跟住佢地打招呼傾兩句，我就係隔離棟係度on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算我唔識佢我都會點頭微笑示好，因為我覺得咁樣只係好基本尊重人既禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有D會好似當你唔存在咁完全唔望你一眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔係老奉要同你點頭微笑，但我覺得咁樣好無禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果撞到另一半/朋友既朋友其實有無人都會同對方點個頭笑一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係係我太麻煩?<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"66318eec3df9a9f58aeffa7747ca06a1b60374df","tid":650300,"uid":96680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"啲人睇唔起人 係咁<br />\n你做左自己本分 就夠"},{"pid":"68f773ecb68e0eee99b599c1ed220a6d97b0680e","tid":650300,"uid":101976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"佢唔應你係佢家教有問題唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73be80835747cec9ab6b8764fed44d23ef7e872b","tid":650300,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"唔係個個識正常社交"}]}